# Latest test results directory
# This directory contains the results from the most recent test run
# Files are overwritten on each run

# Contents:
# - summary.json       : Overall run summary
# - l0-results.json   : L0 (Critical) test results
# - l1-results.json   : L1 (Core) test results
# - l2-results.json   : L2 (Standard) test results
# - l3-results.json   : L3 (Extended) test results
# - l4-results.json   : L4 (Performance) test results
# - differential-results.json : Differential test results
